      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NUGGET ROBERTS (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.75 lengths at this track in a handy 19.97 beating BOBBY BONUS. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Looks to have an edge on most of these. KICK IT OFF (8) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 20.11 beating ARCTIC BELL. Leading chance again. LATE FOR SCHOOL (2) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind BEDALE (20.39) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in this for a long way. BEDALE (4) justified the favourite's tag last time and another big run is on the cards.",
